le $\\Delta m_{21}^2$ could be\ndetermined to within 4%, with just 3 KTy exposure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Apr 2008 16:08:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-05-01"}
