ite, but it does not matter\nwhether it becomes a satellite of a small (Milky Way sized) halo, or of a\nmassive cluster. We discuss the implication of this `dearth' of environment\ndependence for the physical processes responsible for transforming satellite\ngalaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 May 2008 09:18:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-05-02"}
